 bili su godinama otpori

921
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:07,280
 iz niza,

922
00:37:07,280 --> 00:37:08,320
 opet ponavljam,

923
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:09,500
 ne moramo se složiti

924
00:37:09,500 --> 00:37:10,200
 s argumentima,

925
00:37:10,200 --> 00:37:10,980
 ali na neki način

926
00:37:10,980 --> 00:37:11,820
 i razumljivi,

927
00:37:11,820 --> 00:37:13,680
 ali u prvo sami smislu,

928
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:14,900
