930
00:37:16,660 --> 00:37:17,800
 ali i uključivo,

931
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:18,200
 dakle,

932
00:37:18,200 --> 00:37:19,360
 i to sigurnostno obrazovanje

933
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:20,660
 na razine opće populacije.

934
00:37:20,660 --> 00:37:21,740
 Ja ne mislim da je,

935
00:37:21,740 --> 00:37:23,440
 da, da, da,

936
00:37:23,440 --> 00:37:25,300
 ovaj jedini model je

937
00:37:25,300 --> 00:37:27,660
 jedini koji je primjeren.

938
00:37:27,660 --> 00:37:29,460
 Meni se čini da taj model

939
00:37:29,460 --> 00:37:31,520
 treba biti puno širije,

940
00:37:31,520 --> 00:37:32,060
 naprosto,

941
00:37:32,060 --> 00:37:33,700
 i ne samo u pogledu

942
00:37:33,700 --> 00:37:34,840
 vojnijeg ugrožavanja,

943
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:36,480
 u pogledu ugrožavanja generalno,

944
00:37:36,480 --> 00:37:38,300
 koja su sve kompleksnija,

945
00:37:38,300 --> 00:37:39,380
 sve nepredvidivija,

946
00:37:39,380 --> 00:37:41,000
 ali da nam treba

947
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:42,020
 i sigurnostno obrazovanje

948
00:37:42,020 --> 00:37:43,660
 puno šireg karaktera

949
00:37:43,660 --> 00:37:45,980
 i na puno nižim razinama,

950
00:37:45,980 --> 00:37:46,840
 dakle,

951
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:48,820
 dobi populacije u Hradsku.

952
00:37:48,820 --> 00:37:50,620
 A kako potaknut mlade?

953
00:37:50,620 --> 00:37:53,880
 Na narazumijevanje tako toga?

954
00:37:53,880 --> 00:37:55,280
 Pa čak i nas malo starije,

955
00:37:55,280 --> 00:37:57,300
 jer kad vi nešto tako predložite

956
00:37:57,300 --> 00:37:57,880
 u medijima,

957
00:37:57,880 --> 00:37:59,340
 odmah hrpa komentara,

958
00:37:59,340 --> 00:38:00,560
 a, znate one,

959
00:38:00,560 --> 00:38:02,240
 neka ovi dezeteri,

960
00:38:02,240 --> 00:38:03,080
 neka,

961
00:38:03,080 --> 00:38:03,700
 okej,

962
00:38:03,700 --> 00:38:04,920
 svatko ima pravo na svoju,

963
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:05,160
 ali,

964
00:38:05,160 --> 00:38:05,920
