965
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:07,080
 A situacija oko nas,

966
00:38:07,080 --> 00:38:07,960
 i sami ste rekli,

967
00:38:07,960 --> 00:38:08,380
 ne znao vi,

968
00:38:08,380 --> 00:38:09,860
 je vrlo, vrlo ozbiljna.

969
00:38:09,860 --> 00:38:10,160
 Dakle,

970
00:38:10,160 --> 00:38:12,320
 to vam je uvijek tipično,

971
00:38:12,420 --> 00:38:14,540
