 vrlo, kako bih ja rekao,

975
00:38:21,460 --> 00:38:25,000
 jedan nevjerojatno kompleksan fenomen,

976
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:25,800
 teorijski,

977
00:38:25,800 --> 00:38:27,020
 ali i empirijski.

978
00:38:27,020 --> 00:38:28,080
 Jel?

979
00:38:28,080 --> 00:38:29,120
 Dakle,

980
00:38:29,120 --> 00:38:30,020
 i

981
00:38:30,020 --> 00:38:33,820
 fon ima jednu svoju specifičnost,

982
00:38:33,820 --> 00:38:34,580
 šta to je,

983
00:38:34,580 --> 00:38:35,860
 da,

984
00:38:35,860 --> 00:38:36,840
 ovaj,

985
00:38:36,840 --> 00:38:39,360
 uvijek imamo relativističke stave,

986
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:40,620
 prema sigurnosti,

987
00:38:40,620 --> 00:38:41,000
