990
00:38:44,600 --> 00:38:47,360
 uvijek imamo relativizaciju rizika.

991
00:38:47,360 --> 00:38:48,020
 Neće mene.

992
00:38:48,020 --> 00:38:48,740
 Da.

993
00:38:48,740 --> 00:38:49,580
 Neće, jel?

994
00:38:49,580 --> 00:38:50,640
 Dobro,

995
00:38:50,640 --> 00:38:51,200
 ovaj,

996
00:38:51,200 --> 00:38:54,000
 imamo neki način ignoriranje rizika,

997
00:38:54,000 --> 00:38:54,380
 jel?

998
00:38:54,380 --> 00:38:55,700
 Ono što,

999
00:38:55,700 --> 00:38:56,280
 ovaj,

1000
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:57,320
 s druge strane,

1001
00:38:57,320 --> 00:39:00,360
 ne pobitno znamo što je sigurnost,

1002
00:39:00,940 --> 00:39:02,560
 a to je empirijski,

1003
00:39:02,560 --> 00:39:03,500
 onda kada izgubimo.

1004
00:39:03,500 --> 00:39:05,540
 E, onda više nikog ne pita.

1005
00:39:05,540 --> 00:39:08,460
 E, zato sigurnost ima sasvim drugu ulogu,

1006
00:39:08,460 --> 00:39:09,080
 jel?

1007
00:39:09,080 --> 00:39:10,580
 Dakle, da je ne izgubimo.

1008
00:39:10,580 --> 00:39:15,380
 Dakle, sigurnost u svojoj biti je temeljna socijalna potreba.

1009
00:39:15,380 --> 00:39:17,160
 Temeljna socijalna potreba.

1010
00:39:17,160 --> 00:39:19,680
 To znači što je jedan znameniti kancelar,

1011
00:39:19,680 --> 00:39:20,900
 još pređe 80 godina,

1012
00:39:20,900 --> 00:39:22,300
 kada Aden Auer kazao,

1013
00:39:22,300 --> 00:39:23,880
 sigurnost nije sve,

1014
00:39:23,880 --> 00:39:25,900
 ali sve ostalo bez sigurnosti je ništa.

1015
00:39:25,900 --> 00:39:26,220
 Da.

1016
00:39:26,220 --> 00:39:29,580
 I ja bih rekao da je to ne pobitnom polazište,

1017
00:39:30,120 --> 00:39:31,800
 a da sve ostalo vam je stvar,

1018
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:32,760
 ja bih rekao,

1019
00:39:32,760 --> 00:39:33,900
 prvo ekspertiza,

1020
00:39:33,900 --> 00:39:35,520
 ali i tehnika,

1021
00:39:35,520 --> 00:39:38,140
 ali i svačanja svega toga zajedla.

1022
00:39:38,140 --> 00:39:39,600
 Dakle, svačanja, jel?

1023
00:39:39,600 --> 00:39:43,080
 I onda imate postupne,

1024
00:39:43,080 --> 00:39:43,920
 ja bih rekao,

1025
00:39:43,920 --> 00:39:47,240
 modele za implementaciju toga.

1026
00:39:47,240 --> 00:39:49,200
 Uvijek vam je to spoj,

1027
00:39:49,200 --> 00:39:49,640
 dakle,

1028
00:39:49,640 --> 00:39:50,540
 edukacije,

1029
00:39:50,540 --> 00:39:51,880
 jednog tipa,

1030
00:39:51,880 --> 00:39:52,240
 dakle,

1031
00:39:52,240 --> 00:39:53,500
 znamstveno-teorijskog,

1032
00:39:53,500 --> 00:39:53,620
 jel?

1033
00:39:53,620 --> 00:39:55,280
 i drugo od treninga,

1034
00:39:55,280 --> 00:39:55,500
 jel?

1035
00:39:55,500 --> 00:39:56,720
 I naravno,

1036
00:39:56,720 --> 00:39:58,520
 da bi to sve skupa mogli napraviti,

1037
00:39:58,520 --> 00:39:59,640
 morate ima razvoj svijesti.

1038
00:39:59,640 --> 00:40:01,260
 Razvoj svijesti.

1039
00:40:01,260 --> 00:40:02,980
 Najteže je razviti svijest,

1040
00:40:02,980 --> 00:40:04,500
 jer naravno da,

1041
00:40:04,500 --> 00:40:05,080
 ha, gledajte,

1042
00:40:05,080 --> 00:40:06,680
