1043
00:40:06,680 --> 00:40:07,440
 kad sam siguran?

1044
00:40:07,520 --> 00:40:08,360
 To su vam tipični,

1045
00:40:08,360 --> 00:40:10,560
 ignoransko-aroganski pristup

1046
00:40:10,560 --> 00:40:11,860
 i pojedinaca i društva.

1047
00:40:11,860 --> 00:40:13,140
 Uzmite firme,

1048
00:40:13,140 --> 00:40:13,820
 ako hoćete,

1049
00:40:13,820 --> 00:40:13,960
 jel?

1050
00:40:13,960 --> 00:40:15,540
 Uvijek vam je sukop,

1051
00:40:15,540 --> 00:40:15,760
 jel?

1052
00:40:15,760 --> 00:40:16,960
 Sada se pojavilo nešto

1053
00:40:16,960 --> 00:40:17,660
 što je logično,

1054
00:40:17,660 --> 00:40:17,800
 jel?

1055
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:19,180
 Zadnjih desetljedeća što se zove

1056
00:40:19,180 --> 00:40:21,240
