1057
00:40:21,240 --> 00:40:21,600
 Sigurno, da.

1058
00:40:21,600 --> 00:40:22,020
 Jel?

1059
00:40:22,020 --> 00:40:22,880
 To je, dakle,

1060
00:40:22,880 --> 00:40:24,680
