1065
00:40:28,720 --> 00:40:29,620
 Vita, nama ništa nije,

1066
00:40:37,520 --> 00:40:37,900
 po mir,

1067
00:40:37,900 --> 00:40:39,020
 ta dva suprotna stajališta.

1068
00:40:39,020 --> 00:40:39,860
 To, to, to.

1069
00:40:39,860 --> 00:40:41,340
 E, to vam je i na razini društva,

1070
00:40:41,340 --> 00:40:41,740
 gledajte,

1071
00:40:41,740 --> 00:40:43,220
 onda se morate baviti time,

1072
00:40:43,220 --> 00:40:44,560
 ja bih rekao,

1073
00:40:44,560 --> 00:40:45,480
