1074
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:46,020
 puno nije,

1075
00:40:46,020 --> 00:40:46,680
 si ranije,

1076
00:40:46,680 --> 00:40:48,040
 na prvom mjestu edukacija.

1077
00:40:48,040 --> 00:40:49,180
 A zamislite sad.

1078
00:40:49,180 --> 00:40:50,120
 To je edukacija.

1079
00:40:50,120 --> 00:40:51,480
 Znate, danas odete na zapad,

1080
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:53,000
 vi danas nemate na seučilištu

1081
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:54,000
 ni jednom,

1082
00:40:54,000 --> 00:40:54,420
 jel?

1083
00:40:54,420 --> 00:40:55,580
 U svijetu ozbiljnom,

1084
00:40:55,580 --> 00:40:56,660
 da nemate neki program

1085
00:40:56,660 --> 00:40:59,220
 iz svere prototerorizma.

1086
00:40:59,220 --> 00:40:59,480
 Da.

1087
00:40:59,480 --> 00:41:00,840
 Pa to je normalno,

1088
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:01,160
 gledajte,

1089
00:41:01,240 --> 00:41:02,540
 terorizam pogađa svakoga.

1090
00:41:02,540 --> 00:41:03,760
 Svakoga.

1091
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:05,880
 Terorizam je civilno područje.

1092
00:41:05,880 --> 00:41:08,340
 Jel, to vam daleko ode,

1093
00:41:08,340 --> 00:41:09,400
 sad što nešto,

1094
00:41:09,400 --> 00:41:10,660
