1097
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:14,780
 pa ponešto malo znam,

1098
00:41:14,780 --> 00:41:15,520
 jel,

1099
00:41:15,520 --> 00:41:16,980
 najveći postadak,

1100
00:41:16,980 --> 00:41:18,100
 dvije trećine terorista

1101
00:41:18,100 --> 00:41:19,140
 vam postanu teroristi

1102
00:41:19,140 --> 00:41:20,500
 u procesu na socijalizaciji

1103
00:41:20,500 --> 00:41:21,360
 u fakultetskoj dobi.

1104
00:41:21,360 --> 00:41:24,620
 U fakultetskoj dobi.

1105
00:41:24,620 --> 00:41:25,960
 Pa onda je logično

1106
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:26,920
 da fakulteti

1107
00:41:26,920 --> 00:41:29,360
 imaju i kao organizacije,

1108
00:41:29,360 --> 00:41:31,160
 ali u smislu ovog temeljnog biznisa,

1109
00:41:31,240 --> 00:41:32,800
 kor biznisa ulogu

1110
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:34,360
 dakle u prototerorizmu.

1111
00:41:34,360 --> 00:41:36,480
 I fakulteti su i mete.

1112
00:41:36,480 --> 00:41:37,220
 Vrlo, vrlo.

1113
00:41:37,220 --> 00:41:38,040
 Privlašte.

1114
00:41:38,040 --> 00:41:38,360
 Svašta.

1115
00:41:38,360 --> 00:41:38,920
 Svašta.

1116
00:41:38,920 --> 00:41:41,620
 Oni su svašta.

1117
00:41:41,620 --> 00:41:42,460
 Onda je logično,

1118
00:41:42,460 --> 00:41:42,860
 ali da,

1119
00:41:42,860 --> 00:41:44,780
 najprije morate razvijaći svijest

1120
00:41:44,780 --> 00:41:46,780
 da smo ugroženi.

1121
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:48,180
 Ali sigurnost vam je

1122
00:41:48,180 --> 00:41:50,960
 u tom smislu specifična,

1123
00:41:50,960 --> 00:41:52,860
 jer jedino kad znamo

1124
00:41:52,860 --> 00:41:54,340
 da nemamo sigurnost

1125
00:41:54,340 --> 00:41:55,520
 ili postajemo svijestni

1126
00:41:55,520 --> 00:41:56,340
 što je sigurnost,

1127
00:41:56,340 --> 00:41:57,040
 to je kad izgubim,

1128
00:41:57,040 --> 00:41:57,720
 onda je kasno.

1129
00:41:57,720 --> 00:41:59,520
 Zato sigurnosti je,

1130
00:41:59,520 --> 00:42:00,660
 dakle,

1131
00:42:00,760 --> 00:42:02,500
 zato postoji država,

1132
00:42:02,500 --> 00:42:04,400
 temeljna funkcija države

1133
00:42:04,400 --> 00:42:05,720
 je funkcija sigurnosti.

1134
00:42:05,720 --> 00:42:07,000
 Bez funkcije sigurnosti

1135
00:42:07,000 --> 00:42:07,800
 nema države.

1136
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:09,860
 Po svim ostalim atributima

1137
00:42:09,860 --> 00:42:11,200
 države se mogu razlikovati,

1138
00:42:11,200 --> 00:42:11,920
 ali ne po ome.

1139
00:42:11,920 --> 00:42:12,660
 Ali država,

1140
00:42:12,660 --> 00:42:13,020
 naravno,

1141
00:42:13,020 --> 00:42:13,500
 nije sve.

1142
00:42:13,500 --> 00:42:15,880
 Ali to temeljna funkcija države

1143
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:16,960
 koja ukazuje na to

1144
00:42:16,960 --> 00:42:18,660
 što je sigurnost.

1145
00:42:18,660 --> 00:42:20,520
 Zato sigurnosti jeste,

1146
00:42:20,520 --> 00:42:22,160
 nema nikakve dileme,

1147
00:42:22,160 --> 00:42:23,700
 najorganiziranija

1148
00:42:23,700 --> 00:42:25,180
 društvena djelatnost,

1149
00:42:25,180 --> 00:42:27,160
 sa različitim dimenzijama

1150
00:42:27,160 --> 00:42:28,460
 organiziranosti,

1151
00:42:28,820 --> 00:42:30,420
 u svim područjima.

1152
00:42:30,420 --> 00:42:32,100
 Pa onda to nije samo

1153
00:42:32,100 --> 00:42:33,980
