1154
00:42:33,980 --> 00:42:35,600
 Tako da,

1155
00:42:35,600 --> 00:42:36,960
 ja bih rekao da,

1156
00:42:36,960 --> 00:42:40,340
 to nam treba.

1157
00:42:40,740 --> 00:42:41,740
 A zamislite vi sad

1158
00:42:41,740 --> 00:42:42,920
 uvijest u osnovne škole

1159
00:42:42,920 --> 00:42:44,920
 onoj DSZ šta smo mi imali?

1160
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:46,180
 Pa ja nisam zauđenje

1161
00:42:46,180 --> 00:42:47,400
 za onoj DSZ,

1162
00:42:47,400 --> 00:42:48,120
