1163
00:42:48,120 --> 00:42:49,500
 malo prvi smo spomenuli,

1164
00:42:49,500 --> 00:42:50,300
 neke odjume

1165
00:42:50,300 --> 00:42:51,620
 prema pijućem sistemu,

1166
00:42:51,620 --> 00:42:53,240
 što su razumljivi sistemi,

1167
00:42:53,240 --> 00:42:53,940
 razumljivi,

1168
00:42:53,940 --> 00:42:54,580
 ali neki,

1169
00:42:54,580 --> 00:42:55,960
 pogotovo neki nas,

1170
00:42:55,960 --> 00:42:57,300
 prijevazni generacija,

1171
00:42:57,300 --> 00:42:57,980
 to je razumljivo.

1172
00:42:57,980 --> 00:42:59,960
 Ali jedno su,

1173
00:42:59,960 --> 00:43:00,960
 ja bih rekao,

1174
00:43:00,960 --> 00:43:01,780
 ideološko,

1175
00:43:01,780 --> 00:43:04,660
 politički odjume

1176
00:43:04,660 --> 00:43:05,220
 i stavovi,

1177
00:43:05,220 --> 00:43:05,800
 a drugo je,

1178
00:43:05,800 --> 00:43:06,240
 dakle,

1179
00:43:06,240 --> 00:43:08,020
 ono što je temeljna socijalna potreba,

1180
00:43:08,100 --> 00:43:08,860
 ono što je profecija,

1181
00:43:08,860 --> 00:43:09,680
 ono što je struka,

1182
00:43:09,680 --> 00:43:12,020
